**Key structural carries:** O-POLICY is the bull twin of T-PRICE's adversarial leg (same China fact base; the hedge is real but imperfect and asymmetric in LiT's disfavor). WAT-T3/CHO-T3 route to the go-to-market threat pass as the transmission boundary; WAT-O3 couples to W-CAPITAL; OC-1 (conversion dependency) and OC-2 (eligibility/basket retrieval) open as Round 03 strategy hooks.

